D\left(e^x\sin x\right)=e^x(D+1)\sin x=e^x(\cos x+\sin x)=\sqrt{2}e^x\sin(x+\pi/4)\\D^2\left(e^x\sin x\right)=D(\sqrt{2}e^x\sin(x+\pi/4))=\sqrt{2}e^x(D+1)\sin(x+\pi/4)=\sqrt{2}e^x[\cos(x+\pi/4)+\sin(x+\pi/4)]=(\sqrt{2})^2e^x\sin(x+2\pi/4)
